  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
```

âœ” Removes default browser spacing
âœ” `box-sizing: border-box` keeps width & padding predictable

---

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Fullâ€‘Screen Layout

```css
html, body {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}
```

Ensures the layout scales properly across devices.

---

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Main Container (Flexbox)

```css
