  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}
```

âœ” Centers content
âœ” Keeps layout vertically stacked
âœ” `100vh` makes it fullâ€‘screen

---

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Gradient Text Effect (GIF Text)

```css
.main h1 {
  color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  background-image: url(gif-url);
}
```

âœ” Uses background clipping to fill text with animation
âœ” Common in modern Appleâ€‘style UI

---

### 5ï¸âƒ£ Pinterestâ€‘Style Masonry Layout

```css
